description:
In this gospel karaoke version, "He touched me" will have you singing and dancing your way to salvation! With lyrics that talk about the healing power of God, this song is perfect for any church service or special occasion.
If you're looking for a gospel song that will touch your heart, He touched me "Karaoke Version" is the song for you. Through its unique lyrics and powerful vocals, this song will bring tears of joy to your eyes and a sense of peace to your soul.

Music by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube production.
